description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Administrator – Mental Health Care Home&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;£18,000 per annum&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;37. 5 Hours per week&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monday- Friday 9.00am to 5.00pm.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deepdene Care is a national mental healthcare provider operating five homes nationwide, offering high quality care to people with severe and enduring mental health needs. It was established in 1987, providing services that include specialised nursing and residential care, we are able to provide our service users with a support structure best suited to their individual needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We currently have an exciting opportunity and are looking for reliable, experienced individual with a friendly and caring nature to work as an Administrator in Old Trafford, Manchester, M16 7NX.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Previous experience in a social care environment would be beneficial.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Duties will include assisting in the day to running of the home. Maintain records for staff and Residents using Natural HR system - In-house training is provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An organised, responsible and caring attitude is important. You will work in friendly but sometimes challenging environments, therefore excellent interaction and communication skills are essential. Successful applicants are required to provide an enhanced disclosure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We can offer successful applicants benefits such as:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An opportunity to work for a company who invest in their employees and have recently celebrated 30 years of success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free DBS check&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refer a friend fee&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pension scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-house Training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee Assistance programme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deepdene Care Contract of Employment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If this appeals to you, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please ensure you complete the application form in full. Partially complete forms will not be accepted.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We reserve the right to withdraw the vacancy at any time If there is a high volume of applications, therefore we would recommend that you submit your application as early as possible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
